  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC437">
        <l>taṉmēṟ ceñcol varūuṅ kālai</l>
	<l>nikaḻuṅ kālamoṭu vārāk kālamu</l>
	<l>miṟanta kālamoṭu vārāk kālamu</l>
	<l>mayaṅkutal varaiyār muṟainilai yāṉa.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/242/mode/1up">242</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/243/mode/1up">243</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, iḵtu avvecca vummaiyatu mayakkaṅ kūṟutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : taṉ eṉpatu ecca vummai ; ceñcol eṉpatu ummaiyil col ; eccavummaic colliṉmēl ummaiyilcol vantakkāl nikaḻkālamum etirkālamum mayaṅkum, iṟantakālamum etirkālamum mayaṅkappaṭum muṟai yilakkaṇamākalāṉ eṉpatu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : 'kūḻuṇṇāniṉṟāṉ; cōṟum uṇpaṉ' eṉa varum.</p>
<p>'kūḻuṇṇāniṉṟāṉ' eṉpatu ceñcol; 'cōṟum uṇpaṉ' eṉṉum ummaic colliṉmēl vantatu.</p>
<p>uṇṇāniṉṟāṉ eṉṉum nikaḻkālam taṉṉikaḻkālamē koḷḷātu, 'cōṟum uṇpaṉ' eṉṉum etirkālaṅ koṇṭamaiyiṉ vaḻuvāyiṟṟāyiṉum, amaika eṉpatu.</p>
<p>iṟantavum etirvum mayaṅkumāṟu : 'kūḻuṇṭāṉ; cōṟumuṇpāṉ' eṉa varum.</p>
<p>iṉi, 'muṟai nilaiyāṉa' eṉṟataṉāṉ, iṟantataṉoṭu nikaḻāniṉṟatūum mayaṅkum; etirvataṉōṭu iṟantatuvum mayaṅkum eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : 'kūḻuṇṭāṉ, cōṟum uṇṇāniṉṟāṉ' eṉa varum; 'cōṟuṇpāṉ, kūḻumuṇṭāṉ' eṉavarum; parimāṟik koḷka.	(41)</p> 
</body>
  </text>

